{"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"typedef","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:BFv(#*$objc(cs)NSString#*$objc(cs)NSError)","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void (^)(NSString *, NSError *)"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This closure is called when the device registration process finishes, either successfully or with an error."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The handler receives two parameters:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"token","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":": The push token string if registration succeeded, or ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if it failed"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"error"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": An error object if registration failed, or "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if it succeeded","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration result with UI updates and backend sync:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["func registerForNotifications() {","    let registrationHandler: PushwooshRegistrationHandler = { token, error in","        if let error = error {","            self.logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","            self.updateNotificationStatus(.failed)","            return","        }","","        guard let token = token else { return }","","        self.logger.info(\"Push token received: \\(token.prefix(20))...\")","        self.updateNotificationStatus(.registered)","","        self.syncPushTokenWithBackend(token)","    }","","    Pushwoosh.configure.registerForPushNotifications(withCompletion: registrationHandler)","}","","func syncPushTokenWithBackend(_ token: String) {","    let hwid = Pushwoosh.configure.getHWID()","    apiClient.post(\"\/devices\/register\", body: [","        \"push_token\": token,","        \"hwid\": hwid,","        \"platform\": \"ios\"","    ])","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework"]]},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"typealias","fragments":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshFramework"}],"title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","externalID":"c:PWTypes.h@T@PushwooshRegistrationHandler","roleHeading":"Type Alias"},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler"]}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler"],"title":"Related Documentation"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework":{"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework","abstract":[{"text":"Push notification SDK for iOS applications.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework","role":"collection","title":"PushwooshFramework"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshErrorHandler":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Completion handler called when an operation fails."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwoosherrorhandler","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshErrorHandler"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshErrorHandler","role":"symbol","title":"PushwooshErrorHandler","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"typealias"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS/documentation/PushwooshFramework/PushwooshRegistrationHandler":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler"}],"abstract":[{"text":"Completion handler called when push notification registration completes.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshframework\/pushwooshregistrationhandler","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS\/documentation\/PushwooshFramework\/PushwooshRegistrationHandler","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshRegistrationHandler","kind":"symbol"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/title","value":"PushwooshErrorHandler"},{"op":"replace","path":"\/references\/doc:~1~1com.pushwoosh.PushwooshiOS~1documentation~1PushwooshFramework~1PushwooshErrorHandler\/fragments","value":[{"text":"PushwooshErrorHandler","kind":"identifier"}]}],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}]}